Package maps.gml.formats

Class Summary
Common A bunch of common GML format namespaces and qnames.
GeospatialInformationAuthorityFormat A MapFormat that can handle maps from Japan's Geospatial Information Authority.
MeijoFormat A MapFormat that can handle GML maps from Meijo University.
OrdnanceSurveyFormat A MapFormat that can handle maps from the UK Ordnance Survey.
RobocupFormat A MapFormat that can handle Robocup Rescue GML maps.
